OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778875555
OL,3,C'That's not my son,' triple killer's
OL,4,Cmum told police on first arrest
OL,6,FThree years later, the paranoid
OL,7,Fschizophrenic stabbed to death
OL,8,Fstudents Barnaby Webber and Grace
OL,9,FO'Malley-Kumar and school caretaker
OL,10,FIan Coates, before trying to murder
OL,11,Fthree pedestrians with a van in
OL,12,FNottingham.
OL,14,FMrs Calocane, who gave birth to her
OL,15,Feldest son Valdo at the age of 16,
OL,16,Fspoke about his first arrest in May
OL,17,F2020 for causing damage to a
OL,18,Fneighbour's door.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
