PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778875555
OL,3,C'That's not my son,' triple killer's
OL,4,Cmum told police on first arrest
OL,6,FShe said: "Speaking about when she
OL,7,Flearned of his arrest, Mrs Calocane
OL,8,Fsaid: "When they called to say 'your
OL,9,Fson's been arrested for burglary'... I
OL,10,Fsaid 'he's 28 years old, how can he be
OL,11,Farrested for burglary? He's never done
OL,12,Fanything like that. That's out of
OL,13,Fcharacter. I can't accept that.'
OL,15,F"I said, 'You're telling me he's
OL,16,Fbecoming a delinquent. That's not my
OL,17,Fson.'"
OL,19,FAround this time, the inquiry heard,
OL,20,FCalocane had called his relatives
OL,21,F"sounding agitated and crying".
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@AOUyD@FO]}D@AOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
