CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778875555
OL,3,C'That's not my son,' triple killer's
OL,4,Cmum told police on first arrest
OL,6,FThe inquiry heard notes from the time
OL,7,Fshow Mrs Calocane wanted her son to be
OL,8,Ftaken to hospital and that he was a
OL,9,F"risk to others".
OL,11,FCounsel to the inquiry Rachel Langdale
OL,12,FKC asked: "You were satisfied you did
OL,13,Fsay that? 'His current mental state is
OL,14,Fa risk to others'.
OL,16,F"You recognised that and wanted him to
OL,17,Fgo to hospital for treatment?"
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@PO]tD@KOUxD@AOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
