OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778875555
OL,3,C'That's not my son,' triple killer's
OL,4,Cmum told police on first arrest
OL,6,FMrs Calocane replied: "Yes definitely,
OL,7,FI wanted him to go to hospital. I did
OL,8,Fnot understand the extent of the risk,
OL,9,Fbut I wanted it."
OL,11,FThe inquiry has heard Calocane was
OL,12,Freleased from custody after his first
OL,13,Farrest on May 24 2020, before causing
OL,14,Fa woman to jump out of a window in
OL,15,Ffear when he kicked at her door later
OL,16,Fthat same day, causing serious
OL,17,Finjuries to her spine.
OL,19,FHe was admitted to Highbury Hospital
OL,20,Fin Nottinghamshire the following day.
OL,26,@nD@WOUqD@QO]
