OL,3,C'That's not my son,' triple killer's
OL,4,Cmum told police on first arrest
OL,6,FHis mother described how she worked in
OL,7,Fintensive care during the Covid-19
OL,8,Fpandemic and became tearful while
OL,9,Fsaying she had to put on a "brave
OL,10,Fface".
OL,12,FMrs Calocane told the inquiry: "It was
OL,13,Fjust like beyond anything you could
OL,14,Fimagine."
OL,16,FDuring that time, Calocane would call
OL,17,Fher wanting to hear his relatives'
OL,18,Fvoices.
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@EO]tD@`OUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
