OL,3,C'That's not my son,' triple killer's
OL,4,Cmum told police on first arrest
OL,6,FHis mother wrote in a statement: "If
OL,7,Fwe stopped talking, he'd ask us to
OL,8,Fkeep talking.
OL,10,F"I just thought at that time, with
OL,11,Feverything that was going on around
OL,12,Fthe world, and then he was far away...
OL,13,Fhe was feeling lonely, being away from
OL,14,Fthe family and then can't see us.
OL,16,F"In hindsight, I think it was an
OL,17,Fattempt by him to hear something other
OL,18,Fthan the voices in his head."
OL,26,@nD@bOUrD@AOUxD@AOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
