OL,3,C'That's not my son,' triple killer's
OL,4,Cmum told police on first arrest
OL,6,FThe inquiry heard Elias Calocane,
OL,7,FCalocane's younger brother, created a
OL,8,F"journal" of messages between him and
OL,9,Fthe killer to give to his in-patient
OL,10,Fdoctors.
OL,12,FMrs Calocane told the inquiry she did
OL,13,Fnot see the messages, which included
OL,14,Fhis thoughts of "red rum", which is
OL,15,Fmurder spelt backwards, and wanting to
OL,16,F"hurt permanently".
OL,18,FShe told the inquiry: "I was going
OL,19,Fthrough like a really hard time
OL,20,Fmyself, and Valdo being unwell.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@IO]vD@QOUvD@YO]xD@AOUxD@RO]zD@
OL,26,AWOU
