CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1778875556
OL,3,C'That's not my son,' triple killer's
OL,4,Cmum told police on first arrest
OL,6,F"I think probably that's the reason,
OL,7,Fjust for protecting me, that he
OL,8,F(Elias) didn't mention that."
OL,10,FThe inquiry heard on Wednesday that
OL,11,FElias Calocane thought his brother's
OL,12,Fviolent text messages were related to
OL,13,Fhis suicidal thoughts, not harming
OL,14,Fother people.
OL,16,FMrs Calocane told the inquiry her
OL,17,Fson's "I love you" messages to all his
OL,18,Ffamily members was "out of character".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@]O]yD@GOUyD@RO]zD@TOUzD@eO]
